        <text>
            <body>
                <p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324610" xml:id="d1e163149" corresp="Gautier II, évêque d'Autun 1189 -1223)">Gauterius Dei gratia
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e163151" corresp="Autun (Saône-et-Loire, Autun)">Eduensis</placeName>
                        episcopus</persName>, omnibus notum facio tam presentibus quam futuris quod
                    dominus <persName key="d1e28143" xml:id="d1e163155">Renardus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325264" xml:id="d1e163157" corresp="Curcellarum">Curcellis</placeName>
                    </persName> laudavit et concessit pro salute anime sue et antecessorum suorum
                    ecclesie et fratribus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e163160" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> totum chasamentum suum tam adquisitum quam adquirendum,
                    quod <persName key="d1e28149" xml:id="d1e163163">Willermus <addName>
                            <foreign>Bechecho</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName> et fratres ejus milites de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e163169" corresp="Marmagne (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Marmania</placeName>, <persName key="d1e28155" xml:id="d1e163173">Gislebertus</persName> scilicet, <persName key="d1e28161" xml:id="d1e163176">Hugo</persName>, <persName key="d1e28167" xml:id="d1e163179">Bernardus</persName>, et <persName key="d1e28173" xml:id="d1e163182">soror eorum Margarita</persName> tenebant ab eo.
                    Videlicet a <geogName xml:id="d1e163185">rivo de Jalen</geogName> citra aquam de
                        <geogName xml:id="d1e163188">
                        <foreign>Braanen</foreign>
                    </geogName> usque ad <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e163193" corresp="Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Montem
                        Barrum</placeName> et ultra eamdem aquam pratum de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325248" xml:id="d1e163196" corresp="Cornelen">
                        <foreign>Cornelen</foreign>
                    </placeName>. Concessit etiam eisdem fratribus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e163200" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> calumpniam quam <persName key="d1e28180" xml:id="d1e163203">Willermus</persName> supradictus habebat
                    adversus filios <persName key="d1e28186" xml:id="d1e163206">Girardi de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324408" xml:id="d1e163208" corresp="Benoisey (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Boneseio</placeName>
                    </persName>. Homines suos sive per elemosinam sive per emptionem sine violentia
                    adquirendam. Habuit autem idem <persName key="d1e28192" xml:id="d1e163211">Renardus</persName> propter hoc de bonis ecclesie <num>vii</num> libras
                    divionensis monete. Hoc totum laudaverunt <persName key="d1e28198" xml:id="d1e163218">Agnes supradicti Renardi uxor</persName> et omnes liberi
                    eorum, <persName key="d1e28204" xml:id="d1e163221">Renaudus</persName> scilicet,
                        <persName key="d1e28210" xml:id="d1e163224">Gauterius</persName>, <persName key="d1e28217" xml:id="d1e163227">Stephanus</persName>, <persName key="d1e28223" xml:id="d1e163230">Petrus</persName>, <persName key="d1e28229" xml:id="d1e163234">Margarita</persName>, <persName key="d1e28235" xml:id="d1e163237">Gertrudis</persName> et <persName key="d1e28241" xml:id="d1e163240">Aaliz</persName>. Hujus rei testes sunt
                        <persName key="d1e28247" xml:id="d1e163243">Bernardus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324334" xml:id="d1e163245" corresp="Nogent-lès-Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Nogento</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e28254" xml:id="d1e163248">Leonardus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e163250" corresp="Marmagne (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Marmania</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e28260" xml:id="d1e163253">Robertus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325264" xml:id="d1e163255" corresp="Curcellarum">Curcellis</placeName>
                    </persName> capellani, <persName key="d1e28266" xml:id="d1e163259">Humbaudus de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324355" xml:id="d1e163261" corresp="Rougemont (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Rubeo
                            Monte</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e28272" xml:id="d1e163264">Bartholomeus <addName>
                            <foreign>aus Poces</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e28278" xml:id="d1e163270">Renerius de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324430" xml:id="d1e163272" corresp="Champ-d'Oiseau (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                            <foreign>Chaudoisaul</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e28284" xml:id="d1e163276">Teobaudus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e163278" corresp="Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Monte Barro</placeName>
                        prepositus</persName>. Ut igitur hoc ratum sit et firmum in posterum ad
                    preces ipsius <persName key="d1e28291" xml:id="d1e163282">Renardi</persName>
                    presenti pagine sigillum meum apponi precepi. Anno verbi incarnati <num>m° cc°
                        iiii°</num>.</p>
